{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "第七回　血海深仇。剑客行故事继续。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说！你是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不用担心，他不会死的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我，我恨死你了！……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他，他若是死了，……我永远不会原谅……你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "婉儿，你不用心急！大叔负责还给你一个活……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "活……活人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "噗哧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "少女害羞的神情最美！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "水……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唉！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "情",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谢……谢",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谢谢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哎呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "婉儿！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "臂儒",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "婉儿！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大叔的药也给他吃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这孩子向来是极热心的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不希罕！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "气死我也！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叭！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么回事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唉！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "伤谁的心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他问我……是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又问我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "娘！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别打岔！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又问我展……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展……云天是先父……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小婢不……不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下……想问姑娘一句话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下……姑娘……姑娘……在下……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哎呀，酸死了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白哥，有什么话尽管问好啦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪能……我实不敢当",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "婉妹——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那青衣小婢口中说的老爷子，是不是令尊……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "令堂好像是不甚快乐，难道令尊与令堂……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白哥，请你不要问我这些好不好，小妹不愿谈论上一辈人的事……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要谈他们啦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "父仇不共戴天！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白哥！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无耻的丫头，胆敢败坏门风！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥！",
      "tone": "陈述",
